@ApiService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5436
@RiderId = 1

### API health
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### Record a ride
POST {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{RiderId}}

{
  "rideDateTimeLocal": "2026-03-26T07:30:00",
  "miles": 18.4,
  "rideMinutes": 58,
  "temperature": 54
}

### Get ride defaults
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides/defaults
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{RiderId}}

### Get unfiltered ride history
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides/history?page=1&pageSize=25
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{RiderId}}

### Get filtered ride history (inclusive from/to)
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides/history?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31&page=1&pageSize=25
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{RiderId}}

### Edge case: invalid date range (expects 400)
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides/history?from=2026-03-31&to=2026-03-01&page=1&pageSize=25
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{RiderId}}

### Edge case: unauthenticated history request (expects 401)
GET {{ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/rides/history?page=1&pageSize=25
Accept: application/json